Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.24,0:00:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally found...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.62,0:00:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the peace I lost so long ago.{why is it piisu, is this a danpen joke, what}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.64,0:00:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally found...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.44,0:00:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the peace so long denied to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.43,0:00:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then he came and shattered it...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.06,0:01:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,KAGURA!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.58,0:01:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.54,0:01:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll pay for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.90,0:03:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{op}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.73,0:03:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit, Izumo...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.49,0:03:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvie?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.76,0:03:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Silvie, my terrible smelly wench.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.17,0:03:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I'm not going to lose you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.47,0:03:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The world can burn first!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.78,0:03:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.96,0:03:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has the reaper come for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.91,0:03:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think I'm the Grim Reaper?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.08,0:03:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, the only reaper here...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.20,0:03:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.05,0:04:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's part of their Machine Angel!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.07,0:04:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I hear the pilot's voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.59,0:04:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.43,0:04:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm you, and you're me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.52,0:04:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's exactly why I'm going to make you pay for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.44,0:04:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.04,0:04:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You killed our father!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.45,0:04:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our father? Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.70,0:04:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Izumo, the commander of Altair!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.08,0:04:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.67,0:04:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You took everything from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.30,0:04:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, Amata, you worthless wimp.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.84,0:04:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think you're so cool because you can Union by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.01,0:05:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I can do anything you can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.41,0:05:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't escape from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.88,0:05:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.52,0:05:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we're even.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.14,0:05:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two pieces of a divided soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.83,0:05:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two pieces of the Machine Angel coming together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.41,0:06:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The red dream is about to meet the blue reality.{the fuck, this line sounds bad and makes no sense}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.09,0:06:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chairman Crea, what is happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.41,0:06:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A red planet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.22,0:06:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.79,0:06:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Altair.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.98,0:06:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're detecting Gepard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.74,0:06:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's engaged with an Abductor!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.98,0:06:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.20,0:07:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mix!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.28,0:07:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me in, Mix!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.74,0:07:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spatial Augmentation!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.25,0:07:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Andy, you're not going to get through to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.90,0:07:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you keep using up your power at this rate, you're dead meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.48,0:07:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't give up and leave Mix!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.51,0:07:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm staying right here, Mix!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.41,0:07:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I have you in my arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.75,0:07:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mix!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.42,0:07:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mix!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.15,0:07:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't you leave me alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.58,0:07:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me fill your hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.93,0:07:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate holes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.41,0:08:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I absolutely hate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.91,0:08:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mix!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.67,0:08:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Andy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.17,0:08:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get back, Andy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.89,0:08:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to die here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.18,0:08:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not leaving her now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.18,0:08:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mix! I'm going to fill that gaping hole in your heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.24,0:08:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hole... in my heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.70,0:08:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mix!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.80,0:09:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're finally in my arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.82,0:09:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Mix.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.78,0:09:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The holes in my memories are filling up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.62,0:09:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The memories of when I was a girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.16,0:09:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he's all over them...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.62,0:09:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Andy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.24,0:09:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Andy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.27,0:09:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your memories are back?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.71,0:09:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Andy.. Andy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.83,0:09:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mix! Thank{\fscx200}-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.11,0:09:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.56,0:10:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.10,0:10:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't face you looking like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.24,0:10:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mix...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.21,0:10:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a girl anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.79,0:10:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't bother me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.89,0:10:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if you're a boy or a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.37,0:10:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one I love is Mix.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.59,0:10:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Andy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.09,0:10:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we Union?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.57,0:10:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.57,0:10:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.04,0:10:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.98,0:10:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are gonna Union right here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.89,0:10:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you forget what we're here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.53,0:10:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been saving my purity all this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.78,0:10:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now it's time to let that chastity burst open!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.82,0:10:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long-Awaited Union!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.57,0:10:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.43,0:11:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarion!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.72,0:11:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.06,0:11:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry to butt in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.98,0:11:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home, Andy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.88,0:11:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Mix.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.61,0:11:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagura! You had Mom and Dad with you this whole time, right here on Altair!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.75,0:11:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything I didn't have, you had within your reach!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.97,0:11:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.81,0:11:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was never raised by a father or a mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.63,0:11:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.64,0:11:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was raised by that evil bastard Mikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.61,0:11:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Living with him was horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.23,0:12:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being with Mikage was even lonelier than being by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.78,0:12:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't trust anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.72,0:12:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the instant I smelled Silvie, my smelly wench, I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.00,0:12:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That in all the world, only she would accept me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.39,0:12:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That we were destined for each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.88,0:12:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to kill Silvie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.97,0:12:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to kill each other in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.67,0:12:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give up my worthless parents for that!{literally he said "my parents who did nothing other than bear me" so if you know how to fit that in go for it}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.64,0:12:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagura!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.14,0:12:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the weak part of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.82,0:12:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're weak. Even your love is weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.01,0:12:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the reason we were separated from Silvie 12,000 years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.96,0:12:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.45,0:12:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And even in this life, you let our mother slip away too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.50,0:13:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.96,0:13:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now you're going to lose Silvie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.28,0:13:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.47,0:13:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.69,0:13:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Altair is still approaching! It's actually accelerating!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.26,0:13:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're going to collide. It's like the worlds are following Amata's fight.{dumb line}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.24,0:13:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chairman?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.33,0:13:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the next page being written in the Book of Twin Stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.33,0:13:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As two fragments of one soul call to one another,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.85,0:13:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the two worlds are drawn together until they collide.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.75,0:13:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The old will die, and a new world will be born in their place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.35,0:13:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this new world, Mikage will be a god.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.63,0:14:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the ending you wanted?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.58,0:14:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been watching this world silently,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.76,0:14:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I've been watching you the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.99,0:14:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been Immovable through the worst of times.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.00,0:14:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.52,0:14:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything that lives will be sacrificed to the new world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.51,0:14:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the students of our school.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.63,0:14:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All because it was foretold in the Book of Twin Stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.14,0:14:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to silently allow all those deaths?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.14,0:14:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this truly what you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.52,0:14:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fudo Zen!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.93,0:14:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.97,0:15:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I met Mikono, I felt it was destiny too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.30,0:15:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone who shared my pain, who understood me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.18,0:15:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not all about her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.68,0:15:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's shy, she has a short temper, \Nand she gets jealous for no reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.68,0:15:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you praise her like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.36,0:15:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But always she does her best, and she can take in peoples' pain!{what?}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.24,0:15:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She can connect peoples' feelings together!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.07,0:15:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the Mikono I love!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.62,0:15:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not Silvie! Mikono, right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.62,0:15:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fuck with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.25,0:15:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.38,0:15:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fate is on my side!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.89,0:15:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fly over my fate and live for the present!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.18,0:16:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikono!{simultaneous derp}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.18,0:16:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvie!{simultaneous derp}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.88,0:16:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Amata, and...{why the fuck is this ano hito I don't understand}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.46,0:16:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop fighting! Amata, Kagura!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.17,0:16:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why should they stop fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.82,0:16:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zessica?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.63,0:16:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Refusing to fight is refusing to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.97,0:16:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to Union with them. \NYou're doing it with me, Mikono Suzushiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.06,0:16:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not Zessica! Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.48,0:16:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am... the Defeated in Love.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.54,0:17:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,24,000 years ago, I was betrayed by my betrothed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.70,0:17:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.83,0:17:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was with such hatred in my heart that I fought Apollo, the rebirth of Apollonius.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.92,0:17:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But though my love was faint, it was not fully extinguished.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.13,0:17:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo wished to unite with me to save this world, and I accepted.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.83,0:17:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was at the height of ecstasy. To become one with my love!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.68,0:17:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that instant, I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.48,0:17:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The very instant our souls touched.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.87,0:17:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Apollo was not the reincarnation of Apollonius.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.32,0:17:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The real Apollonius was...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.02,0:18:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not just once, but twice, Apollonius trampled my love.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.83,0:18:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will unite the worlds as one, and become the god of the new world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.17,0:18:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And as the Defeated, I will trample out love.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.99,0:18:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the Legend I will write.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.42,0:18:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let us unite.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.61,0:18:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be satisfied no matter how many times I kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.38,0:18:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You harlot!{nikuki onna}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.36,0:18:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.86,0:18:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the wedding of revenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.83,0:19:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Noo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.63,0:19:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikono!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.75,0:19:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was Silvie!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.13,0:19:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.18,0:19:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikono! Mikono's in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.91,0:19:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More power...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.94,0:19:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ianthe, give me the power of the motherworld!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.96,0:20:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage! Are you going to drain the whole planet?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.01,0:20:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata! Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.82,0:20:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cayenne!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.48,0:20:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yunoha and Malloy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.48,0:20:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take my spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.98,0:20:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They need your Element power to stand a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.59,0:20:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata, let's Union!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.28,0:20:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.00,0:20:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Final Battle Union!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.91,0:20:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Aquarion!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.46,0:20:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarion Evol!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.14,0:20:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give Mikono back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.90,0:20:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give her back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.44,0:21:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Punish them, Ianthe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.22,0:21:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A dog with wings dare oppose a weapon of a god?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.59,0:21:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and Kagura.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.61,0:21:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagura.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.61,0:21:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't oppose me either, Kagura.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.87,0:21:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Violation Union.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.52,0:21:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Aquarion.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.97,0:22:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh, beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.59,0:22:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But empty...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.05,0:22:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikono!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.15,0:22:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Dark Aquarion...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.93,0:24:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{yunoha ed whyy}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.59,0:24:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a miracle that we met.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.45,0:24:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And a miracle that we could be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.47,0:24:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's remember it forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.81,0:24:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's pray over its joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.02,0:24:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's become one.
